replies.body:
You may consider testing the loyalty of your computer with a trial by fire.... {{item:3751}} 

... actually just kidding. The most likely causes for this are connection based; the way you described the game freezing up and the fact that it happens sometimes and other times doesn't makes me think there's an intermittent connection interference. For starters, run through the steps in [**this guide here**](http://riot.com/12B7oac) for me to troubleshoot LoL's connection, and let me know if it helps out or not. Make sure to test the results in a few Customs just in case so you don't trigger Leaverbuster!

If it doesn't, when you write back, if you can screen-cap any error messages you're getting that'll help me better ID what is causing the problem as well so I can look for other solutions!
